is to bring the rook over via the 3rd rank with Rd1-d3 (it's also possible to
do that via c1-c3 or e1-e3) . It is also possible to play Rae1 in order to
keep the f1-rook where it is, preparing f2-f4-f5. In any case, Black is
already in dire straits.}) (3... g6 {This is another rather tricky move, which
