Bxd4 11. Qf3 {To begin with, we threaten mate.} O-O 12. c3 d5 {This pawn
sacrifice, designed to avoid the total blockade of the queenside after Bd5!,
is Black's only chance. Unfortunately, his position is still rather terrible.}
(12... Ba7 {This is a huge positional mistake as now Black's queenside is
stuck forever.} 13. Bd5 {The queenside pieces won't get out anytime soon. We
