the open file, preventing or making ...Re8 more difficult and taking the
e4-square under control. Now, Re5! is a serious threat, winning the a5-knight.}
(14. Qxc7 {It is possible to restore the material equality, but I think this
is safe enough for Black, he equalizes.}) 14... Nc6 15. Ba3 Rd8 16. Bc4 {
Time to apply pressure on f7. Black's queen has a hard time finding a good
spot as ...Qd7 obstructs the c8-bishop's development while ...Qh5 and ...Qa5
