yourself, I would say I think the best line runs} Qf6 20. Nf3 Bxf3 21. Bxf3 {
, this is when it gets interesting. But, realistically, most of you won't need
to analyze this too deeply as this move 11...Bd6 has been played in 6 games
only.}) 13. Nbd2 {Fabiano chose 13.Bg5, which is sensible as well, but I like
