(look at the a5-knight). The more pieces are taken off, the easier this will
be.} Be7 21. Bxe7 Qxe7 22. Re1 {White wins all the time in the world while
getting his pieces in the game.} Qd6 23. Bf1 {White is perfectly safe and the .
..f5-f4 ideas don't do anything.} f4 24. g4 {White's king is perfectly safe
