options - giving it up, or advancing it. Neither will provide enough
compensation/play for the missing material, though.} (14... O-O 15. Nxe5 Re8
16. Qe2 {White shouldn't be scared of a pin over the e-file as he can always
support the knight with f2-f4. Instead of playing that move immediately and
